org.eclipse.scada.vi.model

Interface GridChild

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Child
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GridChildImpl

    public interface GridChild
extends Child
    A representation of the model object 'Grid Child'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Horizontal Alignment
    • Vertical Alignment
    • Grab Horizontal Space
    • Grab Vertical Space
    • Span Cols
    • Span Rows
    • Width Hint
    • Height Hint

    See Also:
    VisualInterfacePackage.getGridChild()
